summary: HAPPY 56TH ANNIVERSARY SPIDEY! At first I was gonna make Baxter Spidey and Larry Venom because of their builds but I decided to...
caption:
HAPPY 56TH ANNIVERSARY SPIDEY!

At first I was gonna make Baxter Spidey and Larry Venom because of their builds but I decided to match everyone by their personalities instead. Also the only consistent outfit I could find for Mary Jane (aside from red hair and green eyes) were jeans. She always seems to be wearing jeans. …So I put Niffty in jeans. XD

Also character heights are driving me nuts. Accidentally made Baxter and Niffty a bit too tall. …I forget just how giant Molly and Larry are since they’re usually next to Lucy and Boss, who actually aren’t short, Molly and Larry are just super tall! Measuring everything in Vaggies; Molly, Angel, Larry = 1.4 Vaggies. Crymini, Lucy, and Hilda = 1.0 Vaggies. Baxter’s about 9.5 Vaggies… I think I made Niffty 8.5 Vaggies… maybe 8.0 Vaggies? I gotta re check my math =.=

Crymini, Niffty, Baxter, Angel, Molly, and Hilda (and the silhouette wolves before I reworked them into side characters and extras) belong to @vivziepop! Go show her and her crew some support while they work on the legitimate Hazbin Hotel!

Oh and obviously Spidey belongs to Marvel and is Stan Lee’s character and I can’t thank that man enough for all the stories he’s given us! Spider Man especially I think helped a lot of kids growing up!

photos.caption: I think a big inspiration for Larry's character were a lot of kids I knew who kinda retreated into comic books, anime, and video games to cope with life. So the spidey suit seemed fitting.
Made Larry Spidey cuz he's just a huge dork who looks like a super hero on the outside.
I think I just made Niffty Mary Jane cuz it was cute and everyone seems to really support the NifftyxLarry ship XD
Crymini's Venom cuz I mean c'mon what else would she be? Plus she looks awesome X3
Decided to make Lucy Black Cat because they both come from criminal families.
Doc Oc cuz they're both mad scientists with bad luck when it comes to their love life and careers.
oddly enough it never occurred to me to use any of the actual spiders for Spider Man Day XD
